&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an experienced Fraud Strategy Lead to help shape the strategies that protect the integrity of our community of brands and retailers. In this role, you’ll own end-to-end management of strategic fraud initiatives, translate company goals into team priorities, and act as a domain expert across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
