&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree and 5+ years of relevant experience in fraud, risk, trust &amp;amp; safety, or a related analytical field, including demonstrated ownership of strategic initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep fraud and risk acumen, with a track record of refining fraud capabilities and aligning them to company strategy&lt;/li&gt;
